lead_paragraph: Chris Bosh remained away from the team. Luol Deng had to put his own dislocated finger back into place. Dwyane Wade missed his first 10 shots. Beno Udrih departed in the first half with a right foot injury.

headline.print_headline: Dragic Scores 24, Heat Rally and Beat Pacers 101-93 in OT
